snippet.title: Domiverse - How to play - Ash
snippet.description:
How to play Ash

Cruel predator, he loves to attack weak creatures.
Ash is fast and use a melee attack, he can teleport to dodge, to go trough walls and to kill.

http://domiverse.be

Steam store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/598880/Domiverse/
